less = leaner style sheet 
mainly created in js.

use cdn for create less css.
website : https://lesscss.org/

remember less and scss always run on live server
use pseudo element and class with &:
rules : 
.parentClass-1{
    .childClass-1{
        .childClass-2{

        }
    }
    .childclass-3{

    }
}


sass = syntactically Awesome Stylesheet
scss = syntactically cascading Stylesheet

we cant link scss in html file.
from extension download sass compiler 
name : live sass compiler